BAO CAO HE THONG BOOKINGTOUR (FE + BE)

1. THONG TIN CHUNG
- Ten de tai: Xay dung he thong dat tour du lich BookingTour.
- Muc tieu:
  + Xay dung he thong dat tour co day du cac chuc nang nguoi dung va quan tri.
  + Dong bo du lieu giua Frontend (React) va Backend (Spring Boot).
  + Ho tro luong dat tour, thanh toan, xac nhan COD, hoa don va danh gia.


2. KIEN TRUC HE THONG

2.1 Frontend
- Cong nghe: React + Vite + React Router.
- Vai tro:
  + Hien thi giao dien nguoi dung va trang admin.
  + Goi API den backend qua file trung tam api.js.
  + Quan ly dieu huong, trang thai login, popup bat buoc dang nhap.

2.2 Backend
- Cong nghe: Spring Boot, Spring Security, JPA/Hibernate, MySQL.
- Vai tro:
  + Cung cap API cho tour, booking, payment, invoice, review, admin.
  + Xac thuc va phan quyen theo role.
  + Xu ly nghiep vu dat tour va thanh toan.

2.3 Co so du lieu
- He quan tri: MySQL.
- Cac bang chinh:
  + users, roles
  + tours, destinations, tour_destinations, tour_images
  + bookings, payments, invoices
  + reviews


3. CHUC NANG DA TRIEN KHAI

3.1 Chuc nang nguoi dung
- Xem trang chu, danh sach tour, danh sach diem den.
- Loc/tim kiem tour theo tu khoa va diem den.
- Xem chi tiet tour, danh gia trung binh, danh sach review.
- Dat tour theo luong moi:
  + Tu trang chi tiet tour chi con nut "Book tour".
  + Chuyen sang trang dat tour rieng.
  + Dien thong tin lien he + chon phuong thuc thanh toan.
  + Tao booking va tao payment ngay khi book.
- Xem danh sach booking cua toi.
- Xem chi tiet 1 booking.
- Xem hoa don neu booking da thanh toan.
- Viet review sau khi co booking.

3.2 Chuc nang admin
- Quan ly user (xem danh sach, xem chi tiet, khoa user).
- Quan ly tour (xem, tao, cap nhat, archive).
- Quan ly diem den (tao/cap nhat).
- Quan ly payment:
  + Hien thi tat ca payment theo thoi gian.
  + COD pending co the confirm COD.
  + Sau khi confirm COD sinh hoa don va cap nhat trang thai.

3.3 Chuc nang bao mat va dieu huong
- Login/Register/Logout.
- Role-based access (admin va user).
- Logout redirect ve home.
- Neu goi API can login ma chua login:
  + FE hien modal giua man hinh:
    "Ban phai dang nhap de thuc hien chuc nang"
  + Co nut Dang nhap / Dang ky.
  + Co nut X de dong modal va quay ve man hinh chinh.


4. THAY DOI NOI BAT THEO QUA TRINH PHAT TRIEN

4.1 Chuan hoa du lieu tour
- Da loai bo truong departure khoi FE/BE.
- Chinh sua entity/schema/data seed de tuong thich DB cu.
- Hien thi diem den tren card theo dinh dang dep:
  + Bo ky tu ["..."]
  + Doi dau phay thanh dau " / ".

4.2 Dat tour va thanh toan
- Truoc day:
  + Tao booking truoc, thanh toan sau.
- Hien tai:
  + Chon payment method ngay trong form dat tour.
  + Book xong tao payment luon.
  + VNPay tra paymentUrl de redirect.
  + COD tao payment pending cho admin confirm.

4.3 Giao dien
- Header dieu huong + tim kiem.
- Footer luon nam duoi cung man hinh.
- Card tour:
  + Giu nut "Xem chi tiet".
  + Click bat ky dau tren card deu vao detail.
- Trang booking rieng:
  + Layout 2 cot:
    * Trai: form lien he.
    * Phai tren: thong tin tour + anh.
    * Phai duoi: tong chi phi + nut Book.


5. API CHINH DANG DUOC FE SU DUNG

5.1 Public
- GET /home
- GET /tours
- GET /tours/{id}
- GET /destinations
- GET /destinations/top
- GET /destinations/{id}
- GET /destinations/{id}/tours
- GET /reviews/tour/{tourId}

5.2 User (can dang nhap)
- GET /me
- PUT /update
- PUT /password
- POST /bookings
- GET /bookings/me
- GET /bookings/me/{id}
- PUT /bookings/{id}/cancel
- GET /invoices/me/{id}
- POST /reviews

5.3 Auth
- POST /auth/login
- POST /auth/register
- POST /auth/logout

5.4 Admin
- GET /dashboard
- GET /admin/users
- GET /admin/users/{id}
- POST /admin/users
- PUT /admin/users/{id}/block
- GET /admin/tours
- POST /admin/tour
- PUT /admin/tour/{id}
- PUT /admin/tour/{id}/archive
- POST /admin/destination
- PUT /admin/destination/{id}
- GET /admin/payments
- POST /admin/payments/{id}/confirm-cod


6. KIEM THU THUC TE (MANUAL)

6.1 Luong user
- Dang ky tai khoan moi -> dang nhap thanh cong.
- Mo trang tour -> vao chi tiet -> "Book tour" -> sang trang dat.
- Book voi COD:
  + Tao booking thanh cong.
  + Booking xuat hien trong "Dat cho cua toi".
- Book voi VNPay:
  + He thong tra paymentUrl va redirect.

6.2 Luong admin
- Dang nhap admin.
- Vao danh sach payment:
  + Thay tat ca payment theo thu tu thoi gian.
  + COD pending co nut confirm.
- Confirm COD:
  + payment status doi sang success.
  + booking payment status = paid.
  + Co hoa don de user xem.

6.3 Bao mat
- Dang xuat -> ve Home.
- Khi chua login ma thao tac can auth -> hien modal yeu cau dang nhap.


7. CAC VAN DE DA GAP VA CACH KHAC PHUC
- Failed to fetch:
  + Nguyen nhan: backend chua chay/loi startup.
  + Khac phuc: sua data.sql tuong thich schema, restart backend.
- Loi bang tour_schedules khong ton tai:
  + Khac phuc: bo seed phu thuoc tour_schedules, seed linh hoat.
- Loi field cu departure:
  + Khac phuc: bo khoi entity/schema/data va migration tuong thich.
- White screen FE:
  + Khac phuc: sua import/router component va cach run dung bang Vite.


8. KET QUA DAT DUOC
- Hoan thien he thong dat tour co day du luong nghiep vu chinh.
- Dong bo FE-BE theo contract API ro rang.
- Giao dien da duoc cai tien theo huong de su dung, de mo rong.
- Da co co che xu ly tinh huong chua dang nhap than thien voi nguoi dung.


9. HUONG PHAT TRIEN TIEP
- Bo sung bo loc nang cao cho trang payment admin (provider/status/date range).
- Them export bao cao (CSV/Excel/PDF).
- Them test tu dong (unit + integration + e2e).
- Bo sung thong bao realtime (WebSocket) khi payment status thay doi.
- Toi uu truy van review/rating de giam so lan goi API tung card.


10. KET LUAN
He thong BookingTour da dat duoc muc tieu chinh:
- Quan ly tour, dat tour, thanh toan, hoa don, review.
- Phan quyen admin/user ro rang.
- Trien khai duoc luong nghiep vu tu FE den BE va DB.
San sang cho giai doan nang cap va toi uu tiep theo.

